# 🌿 TomBot

A Lord of the Rings themed Discord utility bot powered by Anthropic's Claude AI.
TomBot responds in character as Tom Bombadil — the oldest, most cheerful, and most
mysterious being in Middle-earth — bringing cybersecurity tools and productivity
commands to your Discord server.

---

## ✨ Commands

### 🌿 Tom Commands
| Command | Description |
|---|---|
| `!tom [question]` | Talk to Tom Bombadil — he responds in character |
| `!sing` | Tom sings a merry song from the Old Forest |

### 🔐 Cybersecurity Tools
| Command | Description |
|---|---|
| `!pwcheck [password]` | Analyze password strength — message auto-deleted for security |
| `!hash [type] [text]` | Generate MD5, SHA1, SHA256, or SHA512 hashes |
| `!whois [domain]` | Domain lookup and DNS resolution |
| `!ipinfo [ip]` | IP address geolocation — country, region, city, ISP, timezone |

### 📋 Productivity
| Command | Description |
|---|---|
| `!calc [expression]` | Calculator with math expression support |
| `!remind [minutes] [message]` | Set a reminder — Tom pings you when time is up |
| `!poll [question]` | Create a yes/no reaction poll |
| `!help` | Show all available commands |

---

## 🔐 Security Features

**`!pwcheck` auto-deletes your message** immediately after submission so no one
else in the server can see the password you typed. The strength analysis is
returned in the channel without exposing the original input.

Password analysis covers:
- Length scoring (8+ / 12+ / 16+ characters)
- Character diversity (uppercase, lowercase, numbers, symbols)
- Common password detection
- Repeated pattern detection

---

## 🌿 Why Tom Bombadil?

Tom Bombadil is the oldest being in Middle-earth — cheerful, all-knowing, and
completely unbothered by darkness. The One Ring has no power over him.

That personality makes him the perfect utility bot — helpful and knowledgeable
about everything, always in good spirits no matter what you ask.

